data.description:
This 2 bedroom and 2 Bath condo is a comfy, cozy place for up to 6 people in a secured gated community. Walking distance (1/8 Mile or .2 KM) to the beach of the Gulf of Mexico, restaurants, grocery/drug stores, library and the Remember our Children Community park and community center. The Madeira Beach Yacht Club, is complete with 2 heated pools, indoor gym, jacuzzi, & fishing piers. Located between Clearwater Beach and St. Pete Beach. Johns Pass is less than 2 miles south.

The Rent includes water, electricity, WiFi & Basic Cable and fully Furnished.
